hell_(computing)" title="Shell (computing)">Shell (computing)</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Painter%27s_algorithm" title="Painter's algorithm">Painter's algorithm</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Resolution_independence" title="Resolution independence">Resolution independence</a></div>
